type.description: The type of the event, always `image_gen.completed`.

sequence_number.description: The sequence number of the event that was emitted.

b64_json.description: The base64-encoded image that was emitted.

created_at.description: The timestamp when the image was created.

usage.description: Token usage statistics that were recorded for the image request.

size.description: The image size that was used.

quality.description: The image quality that was used.

background.description: The background setting that was used.

output_format.description: The output format that was used.

title: Image generation completed event
description: A streaming event that indicated image generation was completed.
